[SPEAKER_00] romantizira svoju čežnju,

617
00:59:05,320 --> 00:59:06,539
[SPEAKER_00] na to način od sebe radi Boga.

618
00:59:06,539 --> 00:59:07,420
[SPEAKER_00] Žižek im svima kaže,

619
00:59:07,420 --> 00:59:08,699
[SPEAKER_00] to vam je sve ideološki uvjetovano,

620
00:59:08,699 --> 00:59:09,719
[SPEAKER_00] vi tvrte da ste pobjegli

621
00:59:09,719 --> 00:59:10,880
[SPEAKER_00] od neke tradice o ideologiji,

622
00:59:10,880 --> 00:59:11,840
[SPEAKER_00] od čega ste joj pobjegli?

623
00:59:11,840 --> 00:59:13,659
[SPEAKER_00] Vi ste ušli u novu i šveću ideologiju,

624
00:59:13,659 --> 00:59:14,519
[SPEAKER_00] niste njeni svjesni.

625
00:59:14,519 --> 00:59:15,980
[SPEAKER_00] Upravo jer niste svjesni,

626
00:59:15,980 --> 00:59:17,539
[SPEAKER_00] ste joj najveći objekti.

627
00:59:18,360 --> 00:59:18,900
[SPEAKER_00] Isto tako,

628
00:59:18,900 --> 00:59:20,539
[SPEAKER_00] onda je jednu od najčušćih

629
00:59:20,539 --> 00:59:22,139
[SPEAKER_00] svjetnonazovsko-ideoloških obrani

630
00:59:22,139 --> 00:59:24,980
[SPEAKER_00] kršćanstva u toj istoj knjizi.

631
00:59:24,980 --> 00:59:26,420
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, njegovo zadnje poglavlje

632
00:59:26,420 --> 00:59:28,199
[SPEAKER_00] govori da je zapravo

633
00:59:28,199 --> 00:59:29,440
[SPEAKER_00] o kršćanstvu na neki način

634
00:59:29,440 --> 00:59:32,340
[SPEAKER_00] sinteza židovske religije,

635
00:59:32,340 --> 00:59:33,239
[SPEAKER_00] koja je sve stavila

636
00:59:33,239 --> 00:59:35,380
[SPEAKER_00] u tu neku transcendentnu dimenziju

637
00:59:35,380 --> 00:59:36,639
[SPEAKER_00] i paganizma,

638
00:59:36,639 --> 00:59:38,059
[SPEAKER_00] koji je sve bio stavio na svjetovno.

639
00:59:38,059 --> 00:59:39,059
[SPEAKER_00] Isus je sinteza toga.

640
00:59:39,059 --> 00:59:39,820
[SPEAKER_00] Isus je most.

641
00:59:39,820 --> 00:59:41,039
[SPEAKER_00] Isus je i čovjek i bog.

642
00:59:41,039 --> 00:59:42,599
[SPEAKER_01] Znam da je priznao

643
00:59:42,599 --> 00:59:43,940
[SPEAKER_01] da jako voli Chestertona

644
00:59:43,940 --> 00:59:44,980
[SPEAKER_01] i da mu je pravio

645
00:59:44,980 --> 00:59:46,039
[SPEAKER_01] jer je super knjiga.

646
00:59:46,039 --> 00:59:47,619
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ona njegova kritika

647
00:59:47,619 --> 00:59:48,980
[SPEAKER_01] tehnološkog feudalizma

648
00:59:48,980 --> 00:59:50,280
[SPEAKER_01] i puno tih stvari

649
00:59:50,280 --> 00:59:52,119
[SPEAKER_01] vrlo, vrlo dobro ubada,

650
00:59:52,119 --> 00:59:53,480
[SPEAKER_01] što možda ne bi očekivali

651
00:59:53,480 --> 00:59:53,940
[SPEAKER_01] od nekoga

652
00:59:53,940 --> 00:59:55,639
[SPEAKER_01] s tog spektra.

653
00:59:55,639 --> 00:59:57,219
[SPEAKER_01] Da, vidiš, zanimljivo, zanimljivo.

654
00:59:57,219 --> 00:59:59,699
[SPEAKER_01] A ostale ovako mlađe kolege,

655
00:59:59,699 --> 01:00:00,480
[SPEAKER_01] slovenci,

656
01:00:00,480 --> 01:00:03,039
[SPEAKER_01] je li to bila velika razlika

657
01:00:03,039 --> 01:00:04,739
[SPEAKER_01] u odnosu na Hrvatsku?

658
01:00:04,739 --> 01:00:08,199
[SPEAKER_00] Pa, pa i nije.

659
01:00:08,199 --> 01:00:10,360
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim, bave se sličnim stvarima.

660
01:00:10,360 --> 01:00:12,480
[SPEAKER_00] Zapravo Hrvati i Slovenci

661
01:00:12,480 --> 01:00:15,280
[SPEAKER_00] nisu toliko sadepohalno različiti narodi.

662
01:00:15,280 --> 01:00:16,780
[SPEAKER_00] Možda su mi najzanimljiviji

663
01:00:16,780 --> 01:00:18,079
[SPEAKER_00] novi kolege bili neki stranci

664
01:00:18,079 --> 01:00:18,900
[SPEAKER_00] koji su tamo došli.

665
01:00:18,900 --> 01:00:21,280
[SPEAKER_00] Recimo imamo jednog Amerikanca

666
01:00:21,280 --> 01:00:22,460
[SPEAKER_00] u 70-tima

667
01:00:22,460 --> 01:00:24,079
[SPEAKER_00] koji je to odlučio se majstor,

668
01:00:24,079 --> 01:00:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] će upisao doktorat,

669
01:00:25,000 --> 01:00:25,780
[SPEAKER_00] došao kod nas.

670
01:00:25,780 --> 01:00:27,780
[SPEAKER_00] Lik je zapravo bio u umproforu,

671
01:00:27,780 --> 01:00:28,739
[SPEAKER_00] tako da je za vrijeme

672
01:00:28,739 --> 01:00:30,659
[SPEAKER_00] Dolnijskog rata bio tu

673
01:00:30,659 --> 01:00:31,800
[SPEAKER_00] na nekim područjima Hrvatske.

674
01:00:31,860 --> 01:00:32,780
[SPEAKER_00] s njim sam najviše pričao.

675
01:00:32,780 --> 01:00:33,780
[SPEAKER_00] On mi je bio najzanimljiviji

676
01:00:33,780 --> 01:00:36,019
[SPEAKER_00] i naslušao sam se svakakvih priča.

677
01:00:36,019 --> 01:00:38,900
[SPEAKER_00] Uglavnom, evo, Jega tu.

678
01:00:38,900 --> 01:00:40,920
[SPEAKER_00] To je pravi doktor.

679
01:00:40,920 --> 01:00:41,820
[SPEAKER_00] Da, John Legenda.

680
01:00:41,820 --> 01:00:43,940
[SPEAKER_01] Pozdrav Johnu.

681
01:00:43,940 --> 01:00:44,860
[SPEAKER_00] Da, pozdrav Johnu,

682
01:00:44,860 --> 01:00:46,539
[SPEAKER_00] ako će naučiti hrvatski i gledati podcast.

683
01:00:47,420 --> 01:00:50,860
[SPEAKER_01] A dosta si stranaca i upoznao preko aktivnosti

684
01:00:50,860 --> 01:00:52,519
[SPEAKER_01] u Svjetskom savjezu mladih.

685
01:00:52,519 --> 01:00:53,880
[SPEAKER_01] Hoćeš malo objasniti.

686
01:00:53,880 --> 01:00:55,260
[SPEAKER_01] Što je Svjetski savjez mladih

687
01:00:55,260 --> 01:00:56,500
[SPEAKER_01] za one koji možda ne znaju

688
01:00:56,500 --> 01:00:58,099
[SPEAKER_01] i što ti tamo točno radiš?

689
01:00:58,099 --> 01:01:01,099
[SPEAKER_00] Pa, Svjetski savjez mladih je jedna genijalna udruga mladih

690
01:01:01,099 --> 01:01:02,619
[SPEAKER_00] u Hrvatskoj,

691
01:01:02,619 --> 01:01:04,340
[SPEAKER_00] koja zastupa određene vrijednosti.

692
01:01:04,340 --> 01:01:06,260
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, vrijednosti su neko

693
01:01:06,260 --> 01:01:08,659
[SPEAKER_00] inherentno ljudsko dostojanstvo,

694
01:01:08,659 --> 01:01:10,159
[SPEAKER_00] koje ne garantira ni jedna država,

695
01:01:10,159 --> 01:01:11,179
[SPEAKER_00] ni jedno ljudsko pravo.

696
01:01:11,179 --> 01:01:13,099
[SPEAKER_00] To je dostojanstvo koje postoje

697
01:01:13,099 --> 01:01:14,920
[SPEAKER_00] bez obzira šta neka tamo konvencija

698
01:01:14,920 --> 01:01:16,559
[SPEAKER_00] u Švjetskoj je gdje rekla o tom pravu.

699
01:01:16,559 --> 01:01:19,579
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, ultimativno ljudsko dostojanstvo,

700
01:01:19,579 --> 01:01:22,800
[SPEAKER_00] više dimenzionalni rast i razvoj čovjeka.

701
01:01:22,800 --> 01:01:24,119
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, ne čovjek koji se svodi

702
01:01:24,119 --> 01:01:25,579
[SPEAKER_00] samo na jednu dimenziju žitka

703
01:01:25,579 --> 01:01:26,719
[SPEAKER_00] ili seksualnu dimenziju,

704
01:01:26,719 --> 01:01:28,239
[SPEAKER_00] već čovjek koji ima i svoju emotivnu

705
01:01:28,239 --> 01:01:29,199
[SPEAKER_00] i kulturnu stranu,

706
01:01:29,199 --> 01:01:31,199
[SPEAKER_00] koji ima i svoju psihičku stranu.

707
01:01:31,199 --> 01:01:32,960
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, čovjek koji je više dimenzionalno

708
01:01:32,960 --> 01:01:33,900
[SPEAKER_00] kompleksno biće,

709
01:01:34,099 --> 01:01:35,599
[SPEAKER_00] a ne neki objekt u nečijoj igri.

710
01:01:35,599 --> 01:01:38,400
[SPEAKER_00] Isto tako, tu su i vrijednosti

711
01:01:38,400 --> 01:01:40,940
[SPEAKER_00] ljudskog života od začeća

712
01:01:40,940 --> 01:01:42,519
[SPEAKER_00] do prirodne smrti.

713
01:01:42,519 --> 01:01:45,579
[SPEAKER_00] U okviru tih vrijednosti,

714
01:01:45,579 --> 01:01:46,920
[SPEAKER_00] Svjetki savjez mladih

715
01:01:46,920 --> 01:01:48,679
[SPEAKER_00] održava neke međunarodne

716
01:01:48,679 --> 01:01:50,139
[SPEAKER_00] i lokalne događaje.

717
01:01:50,139 --> 01:01:51,119
[SPEAKER_00] Recimo, ajde sad prošli,

718
01:01:51,119 --> 01:01:52,059
[SPEAKER_00] tijan ili kad pretprošli,

719
01:01:52,059 --> 01:01:54,659
[SPEAKER_00] je bio jedan događaj Vaja Week

720
01:01:54,659 --> 01:01:56,059
[SPEAKER_00] gdje smo imali predavanja.

721
01:01:56,059 --> 01:01:57,280
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim, ja osobno nisam puno bio

722
01:01:57,280 --> 01:01:58,079
[SPEAKER_00] angađen oko toga,

723
01:01:58,079 --> 01:02:00,079
[SPEAKER_00] ali kolege koji su genialci jesu,

724
01:02:00,079 --> 01:02:01,940
[SPEAKER_00] tako da imali smo predavanje

725
01:02:01,940 --> 01:02:03,199
[SPEAKER_00] o masovnim migracijama,

726
01:02:03,199 --> 01:02:04,800
[SPEAKER_00] o neplodnosti,

727
01:02:04,800 --> 01:02:06,380
[SPEAKER_00] o slobodi govora.

728
01:02:06,380 --> 01:02:08,800
[SPEAKER_01] Anumjetna inteligencija je često

729
01:02:08,800 --> 01:02:09,940
[SPEAKER_01] na tapetu.

730
01:02:09,940 --> 01:02:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] Zna biti, sad to ovaj tijan nije bilo,

731
01:02:12,000 --> 01:02:12,940
[SPEAKER_00] ali zna biti.

732
01:02:12,940 --> 01:02:15,679
[SPEAKER_00] I imamo, ono što ja radim tamo,

733
01:02:15,679 --> 01:02:17,639
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, edukacije Svjetskog savjeza

734
01:02:17,639 --> 01:02:18,920
[SPEAKER_00] mladih održavaju se

735
01:02:18,920 --> 01:02:20,940
[SPEAKER_00] svaku jesen i svaku proljeće.

736
01:02:20,940 --> 01:02:22,440
[SPEAKER_00] To je meni najdraže,

737
01:02:22,440 --> 01:02:24,099
[SPEAKER_00] znači tamo imate sedam tjedana,

738
01:02:24,099 --> 01:02:25,619
[SPEAKER_00] kad se ekipa sastane,

739
01:02:25,619 --> 01:02:27,739
[SPEAKER_00] svaki put se pročita neki filozofski tekst,

740
01:02:27,739 --> 01:02:28,960
[SPEAKER_00] bude lijepo rasprava,

741
01:02:29,539 --> 01:02:31,599
[SPEAKER_00] stvarno mi užijetak i osjećam poziv to voditi.

742
01:02:31,599 --> 01:02:32,940
[SPEAKER_00] To je neka moja dimenzija.

743
01:02:32,940 --> 01:02:34,440
[SPEAKER_01] Koje se sve teme obrađuju,

744
01:02:34,440 --> 01:02:35,480
[SPEAKER_01] ako smiješ reći.

745
01:02:35,480 --> 01:02:36,320
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da, naravno,

746
01:02:36,320 --> 01:02:37,820
[SPEAKER_00] pa da pači ko vas zanima.

747
01:02:37,820 --> 01:02:39,280
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, ha, prvo je neka

748
01:02:39,280 --> 01:02:40,420
[SPEAKER_00] povijest Svjetskog savjeza,

749
01:02:40,420 --> 01:02:41,420
[SPEAKER_00] to je najjednostavnije.

750
01:02:41,420 --> 01:02:43,139
[SPEAKER_00] Onda druga tema nam je

751
01:02:43,139 --> 01:02:44,559
[SPEAKER_00] ljudsko dostojanstvo.

752
01:02:44,559 --> 01:02:45,760
[SPEAKER_00] Tu imamo, recimo,

753
01:02:45,760 --> 01:02:46,980
[SPEAKER_00] tekstovi od C.S. Lewis'a,

754
01:02:46,980 --> 01:02:48,019
[SPEAKER_00] jako zanimljivih ljudi.

755
01:02:48,019 --> 01:02:49,579
[SPEAKER_00] Treće nam je Sloboda,

756
01:02:49,579 --> 01:02:51,300
[SPEAKER_00] imamo tu još Solidarnost,

757
01:02:51,300 --> 01:02:53,019
[SPEAKER_00] kulturu, povijest, pravo.

758
01:02:54,599 --> 01:02:55,599
[SPEAKER_00] Inače, ako zanimljivi,

759
01:02:55,599 --> 01:02:57,199
[SPEAKER_00] tekstovi ekipa uvijek bude dobra.

760
01:02:57,199 --> 01:02:58,599
[SPEAKER_00] Rasprave budu zanimljive,

761
01:02:58,599 --> 01:02:59,900
[SPEAKER_00] ako bude zainteresiran,

762
01:02:59,900 --> 01:03:02,239
[SPEAKER_00] nek se svakako osjeti pozvan.

763
01:03:02,239 --> 01:03:03,820
[SPEAKER_00] Eto, meni je

764
01:03:03,820 --> 01:03:05,400
[SPEAKER_00] Svjetski savjez mladih,

765
01:03:05,400 --> 01:03:05,840
[SPEAKER_00] stvarno,

766
01:03:05,840 --> 01:03:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] draga lokacija.

767
01:03:07,000 --> 01:03:07,860
[SPEAKER_00] I odruga,

768
01:03:07,860 --> 01:03:09,699
[SPEAKER_00] puno ljudi se iskreno daje.

769
01:03:09,699 --> 01:03:10,260
[SPEAKER_00] Zato tu

770
01:03:10,260 --> 01:03:12,820
[SPEAKER_00] imamo vodstvo našeg Mislava,

771
01:03:12,820 --> 01:03:14,519
[SPEAKER_00] Milu i Klaru.

772
01:03:15,019 --> 01:03:16,239
[SPEAKER_00] stvarno su super ljudi.

773
01:03:16,239 --> 01:03:18,119
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da...

774
01:03:18,119 --> 01:03:18,579
[SPEAKER_01] E, iskreno,

775
01:03:18,579 --> 01:03:19,780
[SPEAKER_01] još nisam nikog upoznal

776
01:03:19,780 --> 01:03:20,860
[SPEAKER_01] iz Svjetskog savjeza mladih.

777
01:03:20,860 --> 01:03:21,719
[SPEAKER_01] Ne znam ih previše,

778
01:03:21,719 --> 01:03:22,800
[SPEAKER_01] ali sve koje sam upoznal

779
01:03:22,800 --> 01:03:23,519
[SPEAKER_01] su stvarno,

780
01:03:23,519 --> 01:03:24,500
[SPEAKER_01] ono,

781
01:03:24,500 --> 01:03:25,599
[SPEAKER_01] genijalni ljudi.

782
01:03:25,599 --> 01:03:26,099
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da,

783
01:03:26,099 --> 01:03:27,219
[SPEAKER_01] ima tu nešto,

784
01:03:27,219 --> 01:03:28,260
[SPEAKER_01] svakavan čast.

785
01:03:28,260 --> 01:03:31,420
[SPEAKER_01] A osim Svjetskog savjeza mladih,

786
01:03:31,420 --> 01:03:32,659
[SPEAKER_01] ti si u još jednoj udrzi,

787
01:03:32,659 --> 01:03:33,619
[SPEAKER_01] to je Atlas.

788
01:03:33,619 --> 01:03:35,119
[SPEAKER_01] Čime se Atlas bavi

789
01:03:35,119 --> 01:03:36,619
[SPEAKER_01] i kad ti to sve stigneš?

790
01:03:36,619 --> 01:03:38,500
[SPEAKER_00] Pa eto, živi se.

791
01:03:38,500 --> 01:03:39,639
[SPEAKER_00] Šta vam kaže,

792
01:03:39,639 --> 01:03:40,559
[SPEAKER_00] nađe se vremena.

793
01:03:40,559 --> 01:03:41,719
[SPEAKER_00] Pa Atlas,

794
01:03:41,719 --> 01:03:43,059
[SPEAKER_00] konkretno,

795
01:03:43,119 --> 01:03:44,179
[SPEAKER_00] to je jedna inicijativa

796
01:03:44,179 --> 01:03:46,679
[SPEAKER_00] koju je započelo nekoliko nas

797
01:03:46,679 --> 01:03:47,760
[SPEAKER_00] sa hrvatskih studija.

798
01:03:47,760 --> 01:03:48,039
[SPEAKER_00] Znači,

799
01:03:48,039 --> 01:03:49,079
[SPEAKER_00] htjeli smo organizirati

800
01:03:49,079 --> 01:03:49,820
[SPEAKER_00] jednu prestižnu,

801
01:03:49,820 --> 01:03:51,079
[SPEAKER_00] kvalitetnu konferenciju

802
01:03:51,079 --> 01:03:52,519
[SPEAKER_00] koja će se baviti pitanjima

803
01:03:52,519 --> 01:03:53,920
[SPEAKER_00] do kojih nam je istinski stalo.

804
01:03:53,920 --> 01:03:56,219
[SPEAKER_00] Imali smo prvu godinu konferenciju

805
01:03:56,219 --> 01:03:57,760
[SPEAKER_00] u prostoru hotela Dubrovnik.

806
01:03:57,760 --> 01:03:59,719
[SPEAKER_00] Imali smo onda drugu godinu,

807
01:03:59,719 --> 01:04:01,780
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno prošlu konferenciju

808
01:04:01,780 --> 01:04:02,880
[SPEAKER_00] isto u jednom prostoru

809
01:04:02,880 --> 01:04:03,699
[SPEAKER_00] u centru grada.

810
01:04:03,699 --> 01:04:04,719
[SPEAKER_00] Znači,

811
01:04:04,719 --> 01:04:05,739
[SPEAKER_00] tu su isto uključeni,

812
01:04:05,739 --> 01:04:06,519
[SPEAKER_00] genijalni ljudi

813
01:04:06,519 --> 01:04:07,199
[SPEAKER_00] koji se trude,

814
01:04:07,199 --> 01:04:08,739
[SPEAKER_00] koji želi nešto dobro napraviti.

815
01:04:08,739 --> 01:04:10,380
[SPEAKER_00] Vi u kontaktu smo sad

816
01:04:13,119 --> 01:04:14,460
[SPEAKER_00] bit ćete sigurno Atlas,

817
01:04:14,460 --> 01:04:15,139
[SPEAKER_00] a simbol je

818
01:04:15,139 --> 01:04:16,639
[SPEAKER_00] vlagolješko slovo A.

819
01:04:16,639 --> 01:04:18,340
[SPEAKER_00] Znači,

820
01:04:18,340 --> 01:04:20,239
[SPEAKER_01] nije još za javnost

821
01:04:20,239 --> 01:04:21,659
[SPEAKER_01] što očekujemo, ili?

822
01:04:21,659 --> 01:04:22,320
